  <title>U.S. Populated Place Areas</title>
  <abstract>U.S. Populated Place Areas represents populated place areas within the United States that include both incorporated places and census designated places identified by the U.S. Census Bureau.

U.S. Populated Place Areas provides areal locations for populated places including fields—name, FIPS code, census class, area, and selected demographic data from the U.S. Census.</abstract>
